gpui-terminal (https://github.com/zortax/gpui-terminal)
License: MIT OR Apache-2.0

Used as the initial starting point for crates/orcashell-terminal-view/. Core
mouse reporting, color palette, and box-drawing utilities retain recognizable
structure from the original. The majority of the codebase has since been
rewritten or replaced, including the session engine, renderer, input handling,
and view layer, but the early foundation was invaluable.
